Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.17,0:02:00.58,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's art assignment will be portrait sketching.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.04,0:02:05.91,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please study your partner well, and sketch them with your best effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.76,0:02:10.26,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... my partner, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.59,0:02:13.22,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sorry it's just us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.25,0:02:16.01,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the leftovers, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.01,0:02:17.73,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,At least we can do it without any pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:21.73,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I find it rather boring to draw another girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.59,0:02:24.53,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But... it's quite hard to draw this part here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:26.53,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Which part of me are you drawing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.63,0:02:28.05,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Haha, I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.09,0:02:29.81,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.57,0:02:32.51,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, who is this guy again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:34.28,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who should be asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:42.07,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! I'm paired up with Karasuma-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:45.51,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you. Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:47.71,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you. Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:53.55,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,She said "Good luck," but it's quite difficult for Karasuma-kun to sketch her when she covers her face like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.62,0:02:58.63,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.13,0:03:02.03,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I keep looking into his eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.00,0:03:04.03,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.28,0:03:07.49,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, she froze.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:09.08,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:12.03,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well it's easier for him to draw her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:22.21,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Karasuma-kun is looking at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.21,0:03:25.01,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Karasuma-kun is looking at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:27.82,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me! Look at me with your whole life's worth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.82,0:03:32.68,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, but I want him to look at my future self too, just like this... forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.66,0:03:38.26,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I woke up late this morning and didn't brush my hair properly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:41.84,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Karasuma-kun... excuse me... eh... restroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:43.26,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.21,0:03:48.50,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it, it's all over the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:50.31,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did it have to be today?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.31,0:03:52.59,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yakumo's fault! She didn't wake me up on time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.19,0:03:57.86,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back. Sorry for making you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:04:00.76,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.  It's bad for your body to hold it in, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:02.86,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got it all wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:06.13,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it! Karasuma-kun, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.17,0:04:08.80,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I did this for you! All for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:12.68,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when I say that,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.59,0:04:15.51,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,this is just for myself, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:19.98,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,All I wanted was for you to see the beautiful me, even for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.14,0:04:23.89,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And so... oh, stop it... there's no use thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.27,0:04:26.46,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just draw normally. Right... normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:39.72,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? When I try to draw him, our eyes will naturally meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:42.64,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't! I'm too nervous to look at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:47.80,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! In a time like this, If I just bend my focus a little bit and draw...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.48,0:04:50.85,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What... what is that face?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.20,0:04:52.53,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,She has a weird look in her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:54.44,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's obscuring her vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.53,0:04:57.57,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There! I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:01.86,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:04.57,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,In this situation, I won't be able to draw anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.29,0:05:06.00,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukamoto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:07.58,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasakura-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:10.96,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine if you don't think you can draw well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:15.75,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,See with your heart and just draw with your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:17.94,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,See with my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:21.21,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,With my feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.02,0:05:26.97,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. His image is already in my eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:33.55,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with my eyes closed, I will never lose sight of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.07,0:05:40.35,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end she closed her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.91,0:05:41.91,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The eyes of the heart, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.59,0:05:51.54,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnEraserDust\fs60\b1\c&HE7EBDE&}{\pos(460,160)\bord0\shad0\be1}Portrait\NSketching
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.80,0:05:50.36,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, everyone please submit their work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:54.50,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma! Were you able to draw him after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:56.68,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:05:57.96,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:05:59.35,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:02.75,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nicely done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:06.31,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like... I can occasionally draw really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.39,0:06:07.52,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:14.87,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But why is he looking sideways?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:16.68,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.16,0:06:22.98,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawachika, going to the cafeteria today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.64,0:06:29.54,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Karasuma-kun, how did you draw me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:47.29,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he draw me to be cute? If so, maybe he thinks I'm cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:50.74,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's just wishful thinking! But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.75,0:06:58.17,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see it! I want to see it so badly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:01.83,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.36,0:07:20.02,SR-notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnPalatino Linotype\fs74\b1\c&HF5F4F1&}{\fsp6\pos(230,440)\an2}UKIYOE
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.36,0:07:20.02,SR-notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\b1\bord1.8}Note: Ukiyoe, a style of painting using woodcut blocks. Originated in 17th century Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.37,0:07:26.51,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:29.47,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A love letter to Karasuma-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.40,0:07:33.45,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can at least give it to him in an impressive way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.31,0:07:35.91,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Lack of sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.17,0:07:37.29,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worrying over something!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:39.19,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell just by looking? Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.74,0:07:40.29,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.04,0:07:43.62,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, it's about to start now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.26,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What? It's already time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.26,0:07:47.75,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTMBG John Henry\fs30\c&H3A37BB&}{\bord5\pos(260,450)\alpha&H66&\shad0\3c&HFFFFFF&}The SequeL
