Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.69,0:08:02.70,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKodchiangUPC\fs60\fe222\c&HFDFDFD&}{\3c&H251C16&\shad0\alpha&H55&}Mangoku played by Yakushamaru Kouji
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.66,0:08:09.66,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnKodchiangUPC\fs60\fe222\c&HF1F0ED&}{\3c&H251C16&\shad0\alpha&H55&}Ika played by Shuufuutei Koyoru
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.46,0:08:14.45,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.04,0:08:17.07,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:19.78,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,... talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.12,0:08:22.03,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.57,0:08:32.46,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HEFEFEF&}{\3c&H244A8A&}Yeah! Go get 'em! Mangoku! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.51,0:08:30.36,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HEFEFEF&}{\3c&H7B3533&}Nee-san, I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:37.76,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,An arrow message?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:41.35,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.38,0:08:47.22,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-san, what do you mean by "that's it"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.82,0:08:48.89,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.61,0:08:53.84,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell someone who doesn't even notice her own sister's worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:57.82,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,300)}{\fnTahoma\b0\c&HB15943&}{\fscy90\bord0\shad0\pos(400,230)\t(2800,3500,\c&H0&)}Produced by TV Touto
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:05.40,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnPrototype\fs30\b0\i1\c&HDFDFDF&\a6}{\shad0\bord1.6}The luckiest blood type for today is... A! Just the other time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:08.72,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-san, I still don't understand what you're trying to do, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:11.34,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that bow a little excessive?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.04,0:09:14.04,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A presence! I feel a presence!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.04,0:09:16.75,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yakumo-dono, I shall go without breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.17,0:09:18.76,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.76,0:09:21.49,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch! You will be shocked, Yakumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.22,0:09:23.22,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even more than this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.67,0:09:24.33,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:28.34,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.01,0:09:32.02,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft Sans Serif\c&HDFDFDF&}{\pos(550,240)\frz35\fry310\i1\3c&H333333&\fscx110}Yagami Station
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:44.15,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll get some coffee. For a man like me, it's gotta be a "Sasuke"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.69,0:09:46.74,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you punks! Don't forget the meeting tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.88,0:09:57.52,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:03.15,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Be{\alpha&HFF&\t(1740,1740,\alpha&H00&)} on your toes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.32,0:10:06.07,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:08.13,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.26,0:10:13.18,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The only way to deliver this love letter of overflowing passion...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.68,0:10:15.54,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,... is with an arrow message. This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:21.67,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.74,0:10:26.90,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mangoku is so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:27.86,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A killing intent!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:29.17,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the fu--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.62,0:10:40.99,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:43.45,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.26,0:10:56.24,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If this doesn't work, then from the top...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:10:58.86,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Horseback Archery!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.18,0:11:13.27,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not disheartened...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.56,0:11:18.23,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Karasuma-kun went into the bank!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:20.19,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The target has stopped! This is my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.21,0:11:25.20,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Karasuma-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.57,0:11:27.37,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare thyself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:44.84,SR-notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad500,500)\b1\bord1.8}Headline:{\b0} Great achievement for high school girl! Nabbed robbers with model guns - Bravery with bow in hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:41.54,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:44.68,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No! That's not the point!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.90,0:11:49.03,SR-notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS Gothic\fs56\b1\c&HEDEBE7&}{\bord0\pos(230,70)\an2}Astonished
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.29,0:11:58.58,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so hard to confess?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.87,0:12:04.72,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so hard to confess?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.38,0:12:09.34,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up? You look spaced out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:17.97,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! When you're in doubt, you can always count on your girlfriends!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.89,0:12:20.51,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What? A sleep-over?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.96,0:12:27.10,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I said stop it! That tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.41,0:12:28.11,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.11,0:12:30.51,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is great, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.57,0:12:33.37,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a terrific bubble bath, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:37.58,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a good bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.76,0:12:42.74,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. I haven't laughed like that for quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:46.27,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kind of thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:51.60,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tada! I've brought some barley tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:53.21,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:55.99,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I'm alive again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.15,0:12:57.71,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This iced tea is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.78,0:12:59.56,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's... barley tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:03.21,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, if you don't mind, please have these...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:07.25,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Yakumo! You're so thoughtful! My stomach is growling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.90,0:13:09.02,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:13.49,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, you've always looked after my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:16.26,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse me. Have a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:22.53,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,She does this every time. She's really a good little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:23.53,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we add soy sauce?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:25.10,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And look at the older one eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:26.80,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! This is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.07,0:13:35.76,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really nice when we're together... just us girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:39.12,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Every once in a while, it's great to get away from guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.41,0:13:40.14,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA4B9EC&\fs30\pos(500,300)}Once in a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:42.70,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA4B9EC&\fs30\pos(500,300)}You mean she is always around guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:44.82,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA4B9EC&\fs30\pos(500,300)}A-Amazing really...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:47.16,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA4B9EC&\fs30\pos(500,300)}Yeah... that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:49.01,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA4B9EC&\fs30\pos(500,300)}Eh... er... yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.08,0:13:50.04,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA4B9EC&\fs30\pos(500,300)}Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.54,0:13:51.04,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA4B9EC&\fs30\pos(500,300)}Chef?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.32,0:13:52.86,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA4B9EC&\fs30\pos(500,300)}She really is a princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:55.15,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA4B9EC&\fs30\pos(500,300)}These people must be really loaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.26,0:13:56.37,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA4B9EC&\fs30\pos(500,300)}Right now, do you have a person you lik--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:13:57.86,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA4B9EC&\fs30\pos(500,300)}--ike-lik-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.31,0:13:59.99,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA4B9EC&\fs30\pos(500,300)} or so I say...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.14,0:14:00.59,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA4B9EC&\fs30\pos(500,300)}Haha...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:00.96,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA4B9EC&\fs30\pos(500,300)}Aha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:02.20,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA4B9EC&\fs30\pos(500,300)}Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:03.23,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA4B9EC&\fs30\pos(500,300)}Ahem...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.66,0:14:04.35,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA4B9EC&\fs30\pos(500,300)}Oho...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:05.72,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA4B9EC&\fs30\pos(500,300)}Ahemhemhem...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:07.94,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA4B9EC&\fs30\pos(500,300)}Um... ah... hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:09.15,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA4B9EC&\fs30\pos(500,300)}*cough*
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:42.48,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And the food was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:44.78,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That... er... that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:45.92,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Deep-fried tofu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:53.63,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And the pickles were good, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.71,0:13:55.16,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.56,0:13:50.55,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that! I should ask my chef to make it sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.58,0:14:00.03,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And you know, the taste is rather subtle. My family runs a contracting firm, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:02.79,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I feel like I'm eating food rations every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.22,0:14:05.22,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yakumo-chan's food sure has a certain something,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:07.96,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,that gives people an 'affectionate' feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:08.77,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.77,0:14:11.15,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,B-By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:20.23,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Miko-chan! Say... do you have a person you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:22.42,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What... why are you talking about this all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:24.52,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's so pin-pointed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:29.99,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? But you're not denying it either. How very honest and typical of you, Mikoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:31.53,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.53,0:14:32.53,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't it strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.71,0:14:36.95,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Three people confessed to you this year, but you turned all of them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.47,0:14:40.76,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA4B9EC&\fs42\an1\pos(60,100)\fs38}Really? Miko-chan, you're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.03,0:14:40.76,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,How... how did you know about that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.51,0:14:44.18,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it'll never match my five confessions, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.18,0:14:44.82,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Five times?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:47.52,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure fooled everyone, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.56,0:14:50.02,SR-notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS PGothic\fs66\b1}{\c&H0&\bord0.6\pos(450,550)\an2}8 times
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.79,0:14:54.20,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,About... about that... I wanted to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:58.44,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How would you all confess?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:06.07,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And erm... you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.65,0:15:05.07,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... you see my friend's friend was worried about trying to confess...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:09.43,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,She was troubled and I wanted to seek your advice on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.43,0:15:12.08,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,... what to do when in love, or something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.08,0:15:15.06,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And yeah, it's really for my friend's friend, okay? Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.05,0:15:16.97,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a friend of my friend's friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.07,0:15:17.16,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, she's blabbering...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.16,0:15:18.38,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what it's all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:21.46,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never confessed, so I wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:24.94,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never done it either... or rather, I've never felt like doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:26.29,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:28.51,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:34.14,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What about you, Akira-chan? Do you have any good advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.36,0:15:37.93,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well I can't say this would work, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.61,0:15:41.50,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard of the "Suspension Bridge Effect".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.10,0:15:43.39,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Suspension Bridge Effect"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.77,0:15:55.99,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, the "Suspension Bridge Effect" really works! I tried it last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.17,0:15:58.07,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I've heard about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.23,0:16:00.47,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the way to go about confessing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.72,0:16:03.04,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Suspension Bridge Effect'?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.79,0:16:05.58,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, so, what kind of effect is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:10.38,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}If I'm not wrong, it happens when a person crosses a suspension bridge and he sees someone of the opposite sex...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.08,0:16:14.84,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,His fear of falling down causes his heart to pound.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:18.43,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He then mistakes that for the heart-pounding feeling felt when falling in love with the opposite sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:24.84,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,In short, when the other party is in a state of fright and he sees me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:27.04,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,he will fall in love with me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.33,0:16:30.04,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... simply put, that would be it, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.36,0:16:34.03,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Karasuma-kun, I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.60,0:16:36.61,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna fall.  You're gonna fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.32,0:16:38.56,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.90,0:16:40.49,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Psychologically, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.91,0:16:42.08,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But in practice, I don't think it'd work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:44.83,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's simple to make someone fall in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.07,0:16:46.94,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What? How? Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.16,0:16:48.49,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You just have to be cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.20,0:16:52.58,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But that only works for someone like you, Eri-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.92,0:16:56.32,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be silly.  That's what clothes are for!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.60,0:16:57.52,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dress yourself up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:16:59.75,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a peacock for example! Even animals know how to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.84,0:17:01.31,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it was meant to intimidate others...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.32,0:17:02.05,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's for males, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.48,0:17:04.01,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, like a peacock, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.13,0:17:05.97,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Peacock?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.79,0:17:07.97,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A peacock, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.82,0:17:11.41,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Karasuma-kun, I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.37,0:17:14.59,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.98,0:17:17.82,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're imagining something weird again, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:20.52,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know anything, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:21.99,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, Mikoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.24,0:17:25.04,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where people are involved, it's about the heart! It's the inside that counts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.47,0:17:27.62,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Be confident and go at it with a "Bounce"!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:30.29,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Miko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.17,0:17:32.91,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're absolutely right! Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.17,0:17:35.57,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think my courage bounced up somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.72,0:17:38.83,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,BOUNCE?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.30,0:17:41.51,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Miko-chan, you cheater...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:46.32,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,With breasts that big, you can bounce into anything you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.32,0:17:47.92,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:51.25,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow I think I'm even more discouraged now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.90,0:17:53.38,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.25,0:17:57.55,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. Before I forget those ideas, let me write them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.37,0:18:01.49,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I combine everything those three said...
