Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.26,0:18:09.11,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow this doesn't seem right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.35,0:18:11.57,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, forget it!
