Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.45,0:18:39.00,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Boys are always... always...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.66,0:18:41.25,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,... chasing after girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.37,0:18:44.96,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,All day long, always thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:47.21,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,... about girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:51.72,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,But even so, boys are still so silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.72,0:18:54.72,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,See? They don't understand at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.72,0:18:56.52,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,... how the girls feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.80,0:19:01.52,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there, you silly, silly, guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.01,0:19:04.44,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I reveal it to you, you silly guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:07.98,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! The most important thing is this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.98,0:19:10.90,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,the thing you absolutely cannot take for granted,{}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.90,0:19:15.19,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's the timing after all, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.40,0:19:18.36,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! When you say "I love you,"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:21.50,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,or when you're on a date, or no matter what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.41,0:19:24.24,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, when you're kissing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.24,0:19:27.50,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,When you say goodbye too, no matter when it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:31.67,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! The most important thing in this world is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.67,0:19:36.06,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's timing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.42,0:19:37.59,EndingLyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,0)}Or is it so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:56.05,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes, I'm really late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.05,0:19:57.43,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yakumo is gonna get so mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:20:00.40,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, a shortcut through the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:02.55,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I use it to get home?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:05.00,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Which reminds me, Yakumo said...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:09.86,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-san, don't take that shortcut, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.24,0:20:10.72,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.00,0:20:12.18,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard perverts lurk in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.74,0:20:14.54,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I thought you'd say there's a bear or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.20,0:20:18.50,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-san! A pervert is much scarier than a bear you, know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.94,0:20:21.74,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Yakumo, I will keep our promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.25,0:20:24.99,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Karasuma-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:28.14,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukamoto-san, I will protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.23,0:20:30.32,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Karasuma-kun, you would for my sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:35.65,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it! Using this chance, we will fall in love...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.24,0:20:37.20,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take the shortcut!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:38.66,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnAlpha Thin\fs18\c&HF0F0F&}{\move(370,185,370,285,40,2970)\frz275\bord0\shad0}Switch ON
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.31,0:20:40.20,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.91,0:20:42.43,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I followed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:44.26,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.64,0:20:47.35,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If some pervert comes and harasses Tenma-chan, I'll save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:49.18,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, our love will grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.71,0:20:54.66,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I would probably be mistaken as the pervert instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.26,0:20:57.59,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's what you'd expect, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:20:58.49,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:21:01.54,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too naive. This police uniform will work flawlessly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.46,0:21:04.90,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There is something different about me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:10.75,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:14.23,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! I've lost sight of Karasuma-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.48,0:21:15.82,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What if I get attacked by a pervert now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.47,0:21:21.88,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well if it isn't another stupid high school girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.40,0:21:23.69,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And no one's around, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:26.14,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What an easy target...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.93,0:21:38.61,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurricane{\alpha&HFF&\t(1540,1540,\alpha&H00&)} Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.54,0:21:45.95,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Molesting is a crime, sir.
