Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.28,0:21:52.15,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.37,0:21:53.87,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You saved me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.61,0:21:57.58,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:22:00.80,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Tenma-chan has certainly fallen for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.73,0:22:03.40,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Mr. Policeman!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.96,0:22:05.30,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.82,0:22:07.25,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe how thick-headed she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.43,0:22:09.27,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I look like a cop right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.48,0:22:12.32,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I take this hat off, she'll definitely recognize me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.53,0:22:17.61,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think it's really wonderful for you to save someone you don't know like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.89,0:22:21.69,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be a very honorable job.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.19,0:22:30.90,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my duty...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.33,0:22:34.38,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I must be on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.75,0:22:36.46,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be careful from here on, Tsukamoto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.86,0:22:39.02,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I will. Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.73,0:23:01.64,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,How did he know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.62,0:23:03.25,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.10,0:23:09.99,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A delinquent like me, going on a field trip? Just to create a chance for love?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.27,0:23:12.22,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But why the heck am I playing cards with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.76,0:23:13.96,SR-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on School Rumble!
